 13 		function getOpacity(currentStyle) {
 14 			var value = "";
 15 
 16 			currentStyle.filter.replace(/alpha\(opacity=['"]?([0-9]+)['"]?\)/i, function(match1, match2) {
 17 				value = match2;
 18 			});
 19 
 20 			return value ? (parseFloat(value)/100) + "" : value;
 21 		};

 23 		function normalize(property) {
 24 ﻿		 ﻿ return property.replace(/-([a-z])/g, function(match, letter) { return letter.toUpperCase(); });
 25 		};
 26 
 27 		function denormalize(property) {
 28 ﻿		 ﻿ return property.replace(/([A-Z])/g, function(match, letter) { return "-" + letter.toLowerCase(); });
 29 		};

 31 		function sizeToPixels(size, suffix, rootSize, fontSize) {
 32 			switch (suffix) {
 33 				case "em":
 34 					return size * fontSize;
 35 				case "in":
 36 					return size * 96;
 37 				case "pt":
 38 					return size * 96 / 72;
 39 				case "pc":
 40 					return size * 12 * 96 / 72;
 41 				case "cm":
 42 					return size * 0.3937 * 96;
 43 				case "mm":
 44 					return size * 0.3937 * 96 / 10;
 45 				case "%":
 46 					return size / 100 * rootSize;
 47 				default:
 48 					return size;
 49 			}
 50 		};
 51 
 52 		function getBaseFontSize(element) {
 53 			do {
 54 				var style = element.currentStyle;
 55 				var cssValue = style["fontSize"];
 56 				var suffix = cssValue.split(/\d/)[0];
 57 				var isProportional = /%|em/.test(suffix);
 58 				var element = element.parentNode;
 59 			} while(isProportional && element && element.nodeType != 11);
 60 
 61 			if (isProportional && (!element || element.nodeType == 11)) { 
 62 				return 16; 
 63 			}
 64 
 65 			var size = parseFloat(cssValue);
 66 			return sizeToPixels(size, suffix);
 67 		};
 68 
 69 		function getFirstNonStaticElementSize(element, property) {
 70 			var positions = ["absolute","relative","fixed"];
 71 
 72 			while(element.parentElement && element.parentElement.currentStyle) {
 73 				element = element.parentElement;
 74 				var position = element.currentStyle.position || "";
 75 				if (positions.indexOf(position) != -1) { return element[property]; }
 76 			}
 77 
 78 			return element.ownerDocument.documentElement[property];
 79 		};

 81 		function getSizeInPixels(element, style, property, fontSize) {
 82 			var value = style[property];
 83 			var size = parseFloat(value);
 84 			var suffix = value.split(/\d/)[0];
 85 
 86 			if (property == "fontSize") {
 87 				var rootSize = fontSize;
 88 			} else if (element.parentElement != element.ownerDocument) {
 89 				var parentElement = element.parentElement;
 90 				/* dirty trick, how to quickly find out width of parent element */
 91 				var temp = element.ownerDocument.createElement("jaxtempxyz");
 92 					temp.style.display = "block";
 93 					parentElement.appendChild(temp);
 94 				var rootSize = temp.offsetWidth;
 95 					parentElement.removeChild(temp);
 96 			} else {
 97 				var rootSize = element.parentElement.documentElement.clientWidth;
 98 			}
 99 
100 			return sizeToPixels(size, suffix, rootSize, fontSize) || 0;
101 		};
102 
103 		function getPositionInPixels(element, style, property, fontSize) {
104 			var value = style[property];
105 			var size = parseFloat(value);
106 			var suffix = value.split(/\d/)[0];
107 			var rootSize = 0;
108 
109 			rootSize = getFirstNonStaticElementSize(element, property == "left" || property == "right" ? "clientWidth" : "clientHeight");
110 
111 			return sizeToPixels(size, suffix, rootSize, fontSize);
112 		};
113 
114 		function getSizeInPixelsWH(property, style, fontSize, offsetLength) {
115 			var boxSizing = style.boxSizing,
116 				paddingX = 0,
117 				paddingY = 0,
118 				borderX = 0,
119 				borderY = 0,
120 				paddingPropertyX = "padding" + (property == "width" ? "Left" : "Top"),
121 				paddingPropertyY = "padding" + (property == "width" ? "Right" : "Bottom"),
122 				borderPropertyX = "border" + (property == "width" ? "LeftWidth" : "Top"),
123 				borderPropertyY = "border" + (property == "width" ? "RightWidth" : "Bottom"),
124 				value = offsetLength;
125 
126 			if (!boxSizing || boxSizing == "content-box") {
127 				paddingX = parseFloat(style[paddingPropertyX]);
128 				paddingY = parseFloat(style[paddingPropertyY]);
129 			}
130 
131 			if (boxSizing != "border-box") {
132 				borderX = parseFloat(style[borderPropertyX]);
133 				borderY = parseFloat(style[borderPropertyY]);
134 			}
135 
136 			if (paddingX && isFinite(paddingX)) { value -= paddingX; }
137 			if (paddingY && isFinite(paddingY)) { value -= paddingY; }
138 			if (borderX && isFinite(borderX)) { value -= borderX; }
139 			if (borderY && isFinite(borderY)) { value -= borderY; }
140 
141 			return value;
142 		};

144 		function CSSStyleDeclaration(element) {
145 			var currentStyle = element.currentStyle;
146 			var baseFontSize = getBaseFontSize(element);
147 			var count = 0;
148 			var regexMeasureable = /margin.|padding.|border.+W|^fontSize$/;
149 			var positions = ["absolute","relative","fixed"];
150 			var sides = ["left","right","top","bottom"];
151 
152 			for (property in currentStyle) {
153 				this[count] = denormalize(property);
154 				var value = currentStyle[property];
155 
156 				if (regexMeasureable.test(property) && value != "auto") {
157 					this[property] = getSizeInPixels(element, currentStyle, property, baseFontSize) + "px";
158 				} else if (property == "styleFloat") {
159 					this["float"] = value;
160 				} else if (sides.indexOf(property) > -1 && positions.indexOf(currentStyle["position"]) > -1 && value != "auto") {
161 					this[property] = getPositionInPixels(element, currentStyle, property, baseFontSize) + "px";
162 				} else {
163 					this[property] = value;
164 				}
165 
166 				count++;
167 			}
168 
169 			var sizes = ["height", "width"];
170 
171 			while(sizes.length) {
172 				var property = sizes.pop();
173 				var valueLower = value.toLowerCase();
174 				var isMeasurable = value != "auto";
175 				var isInPixels = isMeasurable && valueLower.indexOf("px") > -1;
176 
177 				if (!isMeasurable || isInPixels) {
178 					this[property] = value;
179 				} else {
180 					this[property] = getSizeInPixelsWH(property, this, baseFontSize, property == "height" ? element.offsetHeight : element.offsetWidth) + "px";
181 				}
182 			}
183 
184 			this["opacity"] = getOpacity(currentStyle);
185 
186 			this.length = count;
187 		};

227 /**
228  * JAXovský polyfill pro doplnění atributů {first,last}ElementChild a {previous,next}ElementSibling
229  */
230 (function(){
231 	if (!("firstElementChild" in document.createElement("div"))) {
232 		Object.defineProperty(Element.prototype, "firstElementChild", {
233 			get : function () {
234 				var elm = this.firstChild;
235 				while(elm) {
236 					if(elm.nodeType == 1) { return elm; }
237 					elm = elm.nextSibling;
238 				}
239 		        return null;
240 			}
241 		});
242 	}
243 
244 	if (!("lastElementChild" in document.createElement("div"))) {
245 		Object.defineProperty(Element.prototype, "lastElementChild", {
246 			get : function () {
247 				var elm = this.lastChild;
248 				while(elm) {
249 					if(elm.nodeType == 1) { return elm; }
250 					elm = elm.previousSibling;
251 				}
252 		        return null;
253 			}
254 		});
255 	}
256 
257 	if (!("nextElementSibling" in document.createElement("div"))) {
258 		Object.defineProperty(Element.prototype, "nextElementSibling", {
259 			get : function () {
260 				var elm = this.nextSibling;
261 				while(elm) {
262 					if(elm.nodeType == 1) { return elm; }
263 					elm = elm.nextSibling;
264 		        };
265 		        return null;
266 			}
267 		});
268 	}
269 
270 	if (!("previousElementSibling" in document.createElement("div"))) {
271 		Object.defineProperty(Element.prototype, "previousElementSibling", {
272 			get : function () {
273 				var elm = this.previousSibling;
274 				while(elm){
275 					if(elm.nodeType == 1) { return elm; }
276 					elm = elm.previousSibling;
277 		        };
278 		        return null;
279 			}
280 		});
281 	}

290 /**
291  * @class JAX
292  * je jmenný prostor a také funkce, která najde element, který odpovídá selectoru nebo obalí zadaný objekt vlastní třídou (wrapperem)
293  *
294  * @param {string || object} selector řetězec splňující pravidla css3 (pro IE8 css2.1) selectoru | HTMLElement | Text | HTMLDocument | Window | JAX.Node
295  * @param {string || object} [srcElement=window.document] element, ve kterém se má hledat
296  * @returns {JAX.Node}
297  */
298 var JAX = function(selector, srcElement) {
299 	if (!selector) {
300 		return new JAX.NullNode();
301 	}
302 
303 	if (selector instanceof JAX.Node) {
304 		return selector;
305 	}
306 
307 	var nodeType = JAX.NULL;
308 	var foundElm = null;
309 
310 	if (typeof(selector) == "string") {
311 		srcElement = srcElement || document;
312 
313 		if (srcElement != document) {
314 			var jaxSrcElement = JAX(srcElement);
315 
316 			if (!jaxSrcElement.n) {
317 				console.error("JAX: Second argument must be valid element.");
318 				return new JAX.NullNode(typeof(selector) == "string" ? selector : "");
319 			}
320 
321 			srcElement = jaxSrcElement.n;
322 		}
323 
324 		var foundElm = srcElement.querySelector(selector);
325 		var nodeType = foundElm ? foundElm.nodeType : nodeType;
326 	} else if (typeof(selector) == "object") {
327 		var doc = selector.ownerDocument || selector;
328 		var win = doc.defaultView || doc.parentWindow || {};
329 		var isInstanceOfWindow = win.Window && ((typeof(win.Window) == "function" && win instanceof win.Window) || (typeof(win.Window) == "object" && win.Window == win)); /* testovani na rovnosti objektu pro IE8 */
330 		var hasWindow = isInstanceOfWindow || (win.constructor.toString().indexOf("DOMWindow") > -1); /* toString - fix pro Android */
331 
332 		if (hasWindow && selector.nodeType) {
333 			var nodeType = selector.nodeType;
334 			var foundElm = selector;
335 		} else if (selector.nodeType) {
336 			var htmlElementCtor = window.Element || window.HTMLElement;
337 			var textCtor = window.Text;
338 			var documentCtor = window.Document || window.HTMLDocument;
339 			var documentFragmentCtor = window.DocumentFragment;
340 
341 			var isElement = htmlElementCtor && selector instanceof htmlElementCtor;
342 			var isText = textCtor && selector instanceof textCtor;
343 			var isDocument = documentCtor && selector instanceof documentCtor;
344 			var isDocumentFragment = documentFragmentCtor && selector instanceof documentFragmentCtor;
345 
346 			if (isElement || isText || isDocument || isDocumentFragment) {
347 				var nodeType = selector.nodeType;
348 				var foundElm = selector;
349 			}
350 		} else {
351 			var isWindow = selector == window || (selector.Window && selector instanceof selector.Window) || (selector.constructor.toString().indexOf("DOMWindow") > -1); /* toString - fix pro Android */
352 			if (isWindow) {
353 				var nodeType = JAX.WINDOW;
354 				var foundElm = selector;
355 			}
356 		}
357 	}
358 
359 	switch(nodeType) {
360 		case JAX.HTML_ELEMENT:
361 			return new JAX.Element(foundElm);
362 		case JAX.DOCUMENT:
363 			return new JAX.Document(foundElm);
364 		case JAX.WINDOW:
365 			return new JAX.Window(foundElm);
366 		case JAX.DOCUMENT_FRAGMENT:
367 			return new JAX.DocumentFragment(foundElm);
368 		case JAX.TEXT:
369 		case JAX.COMMENT:
370 			return new JAX.TextNode(foundElm);
371 		default: 
372 			return new JAX.NullNode(typeof(selector) == "string" ? selector : "");
373 	}
374 };
375 
376 JAX.WINDOW = -2; /* konstanta pro objekt window */
377 JAX.NULL = -1; /* konstanta pro nulový objekt */
378 JAX.HTML_ELEMENT = 1; /* konstanta pro nulový objekt */
379 JAX.TEXT = 3; /* konstanta pro textový node */
380 JAX.COMMENT = 8; /* konstanta pro komentářový node */
381 JAX.DOCUMENT = 9; /* konstanta pro objekt document */
382 JAX.DOCUMENT_FRAGMENT = 11; /* konstanta pro objekt document fragment */
383 
384 /**
385  * najde elementy, které odpovídají selectoru
386  *
387  * @param {string || object || array} selector řetězec splňující pravidla css3 (pro IE8 css2.1) selectoru | Array of (HTMLElement | Text | HTMLDocument | Window | JAX.Node) | JAX.NodeArray
388  * @param {object || string} [srcElement=window.document] CSS3 (CSS2.1) selector nebo element, ve kterém se má hledat
389  * @returns {JAX.NodeArray}
390  */
391 JAX.all = function(selector, srcElement) {
392 	if (!selector) {
393 		return JAX.NodeArray([]);
394 	}
395 
396 	if (typeof(selector) == "string") {
397 		srcElement = srcElement || document;
398 
399 		if (srcElement != document) {
400 			var jaxSrcElement = srcElement instanceof JAX.Node ? srcElement : JAX(srcElement);
401 
402 			if (!jaxSrcElement.n) {
403 				console.error("JAX.all: Second argument must be valid element.");
404 				return new JAX.NullNode();
405 			}
406 
407 			srcElement = jaxSrcElement.n;
408 		}
409 
410 		var foundElms = srcElement.querySelectorAll(selector);
411 
412 		return new JAX.NodeArray(foundElms);
413 	} else if (selector instanceof Array || (window.NodeList && selector instanceof window.NodeList) || selector instanceof JAX.NodeArray) {
414 		return new JAX.NodeArray(selector);
415 	} else if (selector.length && selector[0] && selector[selector.length - 1]) {
416 		/* IE8 can't detect NodeList, so if we have something iterable we will pass it */
417 		return new JAX.NodeArray(selector);
418 	} else if (selector instanceof JAX.Node || (typeof(selector) == "object" && JAX(selector).n)) {
419 		return new JAX.NodeArray([selector]);
420 	}
421 	
422 	return new JAX.NodeArray([]);
423 };

425 /**
426  * vytvoří element na základě zadaných parametrů
427  *
428  * @param {string} tagString řetězec definující název tagu (lze přidat i název tříd(y) a id, se kterými se má vytvořit)
429  * @param {object} attrs asociativní pole atributů tagu
430  * @param {object} styles asociativní pole stylů, které se mají přiřadit do node.style
431  * @param {object} [srcDocument=window.document] documentElement, ve kterém se má vytvářet
432  * @returns {JAX.Node}
433  */
434 JAX.make = function(tagString, attrs, styles, srcDocument) {
435 	var attrs = attrs || {};
436 	var styles = styles || {};
437 	var srcDocument = srcDocument || document;
438 
439 	if (!tagString || typeof(tagString) != "string") { 
440 		console.error("JAX.make: First argument must be string.");
441 		return JAX(null); 
442 	}
443 	if (typeof(attrs) != "object") { 
444 		console.error("JAX.make: Second argument must be associative array."); 
445 		attrs = {};
446 	}
447 	if (typeof(styles) != "object") { 
448 		console.error("JAX.make: Third argument must be associative array."); 
449 		styles = {};
450 	}
451 	if (typeof(srcDocument) != "object" || !srcDocument.nodeType && [9,11].indexOf(srcDocument.nodeType) == -1) { 
452 		console.error("JAX.make: Fourth argument must be document element."); 
453 		srcDocument = document;
454 	}
455 
456 	var parts = tagString.match(/[#.]?[a-z0-9_-]+/ig) || [];
457 	var tagName = parts[0];
458 
459 	if (!tagName || !/^[a-z0-9]+$/ig.test(tagName)) {
460 		console.error("JAX.make: Tagname must be first in element definition.");
461 		return JAX(null);
462 	}
463 	
464 	for (var i=0, len=parts.length; i<len; i++) {
465 		var part = parts[i];
466 		var ch = part.charAt(0);
467 
468 		if (ch == "#") { 
469 			attrs["id"] = part.substring(1);
470 		} else if (ch == ".") { 
471 			if (attrs["className"]) { 
472 				attrs["className"] += " ";
473 				attrs["className"] += part.substring(1);
474 			} else {
475 				attrs["className"] = part.substring(1);
476 			}
477 		}
478 	}
479 	
480 	var createdNode = srcDocument.createElement(tagName);
481 
482 	for (var p in attrs) { createdNode[p] = attrs[p]; }
483 	for (var p in styles) { createdNode.style[p] = styles[p]; }
484 	
485 	return new JAX.Element(createdNode);
486 };

488 /**
489  * vytvoří z HTML stringu elementy - *zhmotní* html string.
490  *
491  * @param {string} html html string, který má být transformováno na uzly
492  * @returns {JAX.NodeArray}
493  */
494 JAX.makeFromHTML = function(html) {
495 	if (!html) { return new JAX.NodeArray([]); }
496 
497 	var temp = JAX.make("div").html(html);
498 	var children = temp.children();
499 
500 	return children;
501 };

514 /**
515  * zjistí, jakého typu je zadaný parametr
516  *
517  * @param {} value testovaná hodnota
518  * @returns {string}
519  */
520 JAX.getTypeOf = function(value) {
521 	if (typeof(value) == "number") {
522 		return "number";
523 	} else if (typeof(value) == "string") {
524 		return "string";
525 	} else if (typeof(value) == "undefined") {
526 		return "undefined";
527 	} else if (typeof(value) == "function") {
528 		return "function";
529 	} else if (value === true || value === false) {
530 		return "boolean";
531 	} else if (value === null) {
532 		return "null";
533 	}
534 
535 	var toStringResult = Object.prototype.toString.call(value);
536 
537 	if (toStringResult == "[object Array]") {
538 		return "array";	
539 	} else if (toStringResult == "[object Date]") {
540 		return "date";
541 	}
542 
543 	return "object";
544 };

546 /**
547  * rozšíří třídu potomka o metody rodiče
548  *
549  * @param {function} target potomek
550  * @param {function} src rodič
551  */
552 JAX.extend = function(target, src) {
553 	target.prototype = Object.create(src.prototype);
554 
555 	for (var p in src.prototype) {
556 		if (typeof src.prototype[p] != "object") { continue; }
557 		target.prototype[p] = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(src.prototype[p]));
558 	}
559 
560 	target.prototype.constructor = target;
561 	target.prototype.__parent__ = src;
562 };

564 /**
565  * implementuje tzv. mixin nebo také lze říci rozhraní, kdy třídu obohatí o nové metody, ale nedědí je, nýbrž si vyrobí jejich kopie
566  *
567  * @param {function} target třída, která metody získá
568  * @param {function || array} src třída s metodami, které chceme implementovat || pole tříd
569  */
570 JAX.mixin = function(target, src) {
571 	if (src instanceof Array) {
572 		while(src.length) { JAX.mixin(target, src.shift()); }
573 		return;
574 	}
575 	
576 	for (var p in src.prototype) {
577 		if (typeof src.prototype[p] == "object") {
578 			target.prototype[p] = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(src.prototype[p]));
579 		} else {
580 			target.prototype[p] = src.prototype[p];
581 		}
582 	}
583 };

607  * vrací konkrétní prvek v poli určený dle číselného indexu
608  *
609  * @param {number} index
610  * @returns {any}
611  */
612 JAX.IIterable.prototype.item = function(index) {
613 	var index = index || 0;
614 	return this[index];
615 };
616 
617 /**
618  * vrací pole prvků určené rozmezím od - do a to včetně těchto prvků
619  *
620  * @param {number} from od kterého prvku
621  * @param {number} to do kterého prvku
622  * @returns {array}
623  */
624 JAX.IIterable.prototype.items = function(from, to) {
625 	from = parseFloat(from);
626 	from = !isFinite(from) ? 0 : from;
627 	to = parseFloat(to);
628 	to = !isFinite(to) ? Math.max(this.length - 1, 0) : to;
629 
630 	var items = [];
631 
632 	for (var i=from; i<=to; i++) {
633 		var item = this[i];
634 		if (item) { items.push(item); }
635 	}
636 
637 	return items;
638 };
639 
640 /**
641  * vrací první prvek v poli
642  *
643  * @returns {any}
644  */
645 JAX.IIterable.prototype.firstItem = function() {
646 	return this[0];
647 };
648 
649 /**
650  * vrací poslední prvek v poli
651  *
652  * @returns {any}
653  */
654 JAX.IIterable.prototype.lastItem = function() {
655 	return this[this.length - 1];
656 };
657 
658 /**
659  * přidá prvek do pole a umístí ho na konec pole
660  *
661  * @param {any} item
662  * @returns {any}
663  */
664 JAX.IIterable.prototype.pushItem = function(item) {
665 	this.length++;
666 	this[this.length - 1] = item;
667 	return this;
668 };
669 
670 /**
671  * odebere prvek z konce pole a zmenší velikost pole o 1 prvek
672  *
673  * @returns {any}
674  */
675 JAX.IIterable.prototype.popItem = function() {
676 	if (this.length > 0) {
677 		var item = this[this.length - 1];
678 		delete this[this.length - 1];
679 		this.length--;
680 		return item;
681 	}
682 	return null;
683 };
684 
685 /**
686  * odebere první prvek a zmenší velikost pole o 1 prvek
687  *
688  * @returns {any}
689  */
690 JAX.IIterable.prototype.shiftItem = function() {
691 	var item = this[0];
692 	if (item) {
693 		this.length--;
694 		for (var i=0; i<this.length; i++) {
695 			this[i] = this[i+1];
696 		}
697 		return item;
698 	}
699 
700 	return null;
701 };
702 
703 /**
704  * vloží prvek na první místo v poli a zvětší velikost pole o 1 prvek
705  *
706  * @param {any} item
707  * @returns {any}
708  */
709 JAX.IIterable.prototype.unshiftItem = function(item) {
710 	this.length++;
711 	for (var i=this.length - 1; i>0; i--) {
712 		this[i] = this[i - 1];
713 	}
714 	this[0] = item;
715 
716 	return this;
717 };
718 
719 /**
720  * zjistí, na kolikátém místě se prvek v poli nachází (číslováno od nuly). Pokud nenajde, vrací -1.
721  *
722  * @param {any} item
723  * @returns {number}
724  */
725 JAX.IIterable.prototype.index = function(item) {
726 	for (var i=0; i<this.length; i++) {
727 		var myItem = this[i];
728 		if (myItem == item) { return i; }
729 	}
730 
731 	return -1;
732 };
733 
734 /**
735  * iteruje postupně všechny prvky v poli a volá nad nimi zadanou funkci
736  *
737  * @param {function} func zadaná funkce
738  * @param {object} obj object, v jehož kontextu bude funkce volána
739  * @returns {number}
740  */
741 JAX.IIterable.prototype.forEachItem = function(func, obj) {
742 	var func = obj ? func.bind(obj) : func;
743 
744 	for (var i=0; i<this.length; i++) {
745 		func(this[i], i, this);
746 	}
747 
748 	return this;
749 };
750 
751 /**
752  * pomocí zadané funkce vrací vyfiltrované pole. Do funkce jsou prvky v každé iteraci jednotlivě předány a pokud splní podmínku, prvek se do vráceného filtrovaného pole zařadí.
753  *
754  * @param {function} func zadaná funkce
755  * @param {object} obj object, v jehož kontextu bude funkce volána
756  * @returns {object}
757  */
758 JAX.IIterable.prototype.filterItems = function(func, obj) {
759 	var func = obj ? func.bind(obj) : func;
760 	var filtered = [];
761 
762 	for (var i=0; i<this.length; i++) {
763 		if (func(this[i], i, this)) {
764 			filtered.push(this[i]);
765 		}
766 	}
767 
768 	return JAX.all(filtered);
769 };

776 /**
777  * @class JAX.Async
778  * je třída, která umožňuje zpracovat sekvenci nejen Promisů, ale i animací pomocí JAX.FX. Umožňuje tak vývojáři plnou kontrolu nad jejich synchronizací a správnou návazností.
779  *
780  */
781 
782 JAX.Async = function() {
783 	this._running = false;
784 	this._canceled = false;
785 	this._pending = false;
786 	this._waitings = [];
787 	this._currentPromise = null;
788 	this._promises = [];
789 };
790 
791 /**
792  * přidá Promise na konec fronty
793  *
794  * @param {function || object} item nabindovaná funkce vracející instanci JAK.Promise || instance JAX.FX || instance JAX.Async
795  * @returns {JAX.Async}
796  */
797 JAX.Async.prototype.waitFor = function(item) {
798 	if (this._canceled) { return this; }
799 
800 	var isSupported = item && (typeof(item) == "function" || item instanceof JAK.Promise || item instanceof JAX.FX || item instanceof JAX.Async);
801 	if (!isSupported) {
802 		console.error("JAX.Async: Sorry, but I got unsupported item: " + typeof(item) + ". I expected function, instance of JAK.Promise or instance of JAX.FX.");
803 		return this;
804 	}
805 
806 	this._waitings.push({
807 		waiting: item,
808 		thenActions: []
809 	});
810 
811 	if (this._running && !this._pending) {
812 		this._processWaiting();
813 	}
814 
815 	return this;
816 };
817 
818 /**
819  * co se má stát po fulfillnutí a po rejectnutí poslední nastavované Promise. Týká se vždy naposledy předané Promise přes waitFor metodu.
820  *
821  * @param {function} onFulfill fce se zavolá při fulfillnutí Promise
822  * @param {function} onReject fce se zavolá při rejectnutí Promise
823  *
824  * @returns {JAX.Async}
825  */
826 JAX.Async.prototype.after = function(onFulfill, onReject) {
827 	if (this._canceled) { return this; }
828 
829 	var customOnFulfill = function(value) {
830 		if (this._canceled) { return; }
831 		if (typeof(onFulfill) == "function") {
832 			return onFulfill(value);
833 		}
834 	}.bind(this);
835 
836 	var customOnReject = function(value) {
837 		if (this._canceled) { return; }
838 		if (typeof(onReject) == "function") {
839 			return onReject(value);
840 		}
841 	}.bind(this);
842 
843 	var afterAction = {onFulfill:customOnFulfill, onReject:customOnReject};
844 	var length = this._waitings.length;
845 
846 	if (length) {
847 		var lastWaiting = this._waitings[length - 1];
848 		lastWaiting.thenActions.push(afterAction);
849 	} else if (this._currentPromise) {
850 		this._processThenActions([afterAction]);
851 	}
852 
853 	return this;
854 };
855 
856 /**
857  * spustí celou proceduru. Postupně se začnou provádět všechny asynchronní operace. Další operace začne běžet teprve, až se dokončí předchozí.
858  *
859  * @returns {JAX.Async}
860  */
861 JAX.Async.prototype.run = function() {
862 	if (this._running || this._canceled) { return this; }
863 	this._canceled = false;
864 	this._pending = false;
865 	this._running = true;
866 	this._processWaiting();
867 	return this;
868 };
869 
870 /**
871  * zastaví čekání na dokončení všech navěšených akcí. Asynchronní operace, které doposud nebyly vykonány již vykonány nebudou.
872  *
873  * @returns {JAX.Async}
874  */
875 JAX.Async.prototype.cancel = function() {
876 	this._canceled = true;
877 	return this;
878 };
879 
880 /**
881  * je sekvence běžící?
882  *
883  * @returns {boolean}
884  */
885 JAX.Async.prototype.isRunning = function() {
886 	return this._running;
887 };
888 
889 /**
890  * je sekvence zrušena?
891  *
892  * @returns {boolean}
893  */
894 JAX.Async.prototype.isCanceled = function() {
895 	return this._canceled;
896 };
897 
898 /**
899  * čeká se na nějakou asynchronní akce?
900  *
901  * @returns {boolean}
902  */
903 JAX.Async.prototype.isPending = function() {
904 	return this._pending;
905 };
906 
907 JAX.Async.prototype._processWaiting = function() {
908 	this._pending = false;
909 
910 	var waitingData = this._waitings.shift();
911 	if (!waitingData) { return; }
912 
913 	var item = waitingData.waiting;
914 
915 	if (typeof(item) == "function") {
916 		var promise = item();
917 	} else {
918 		var promise = item;
919 	}
920 
921 	if (!(promise instanceof JAK.Promise) && !(promise instanceof JAX.FX) && !(promise instanceof JAX.Async)) {
922 		console.error("JAX.Async: when I tried to process next waiting Promise, I got unsupported stuff", promise);
923 		return;
924 	}
925 
926 	this._currentPromise = promise;
927 	this._promises.push(promise);
928 
929 	this._processThenActions(waitingData.thenActions);
930 
931 	this._pending = true;
932 };
933 
934 JAX.Async.prototype._processThenActions = function(thenActions) {
935 	for (var i=0, len=thenActions.length; i<len; i++) {
936 		var thenAction = thenActions[i];
937 		this._addAfterAction(thenAction.onFulfill, thenAction.onReject);
938 	}
939 
940 	var finishingAction = function() {
941 		if (this._canceled) { this._clear(); return; }
942 		this._processWaiting();
943 	}.bind(this);
944 
945 	this._addAfterAction(finishingAction, finishingAction);
946 };
947 
948 JAX.Async.prototype._clear = function() {
949 	this._waitings = [];
950 	this._currentPromise = null;
951 	this._promises = [];
952 	this._running = false;
953 	this._pending = false;
954 };
955 
956 JAX.Async.prototype._addAfterAction = function(onFulfill, onReject) {
957 	if (this._currentPromise instanceof JAX.Async) {
958 		this._currentPromise.after(onFulfill, onReject);
959 		return;
960 	}
961 	this._currentPromise.then(onFulfill, onReject);
962 };

969 /**
970  * @class JAX.IListening
971  * tvoří rozhrani implementujicí práci s navěšováním a odvěšováním událostí
972  */
973 JAX.IListening = function() {};
974 
975 JAX.IListening._listeners = {};
976 
977 /**
978  * navěsí posluchač události na element a vrátí instanci JAX.Listener. Při vyvolání události pak do funkce předává jako parametr instanci JAX.Event.
979  *
980  * @param {string} type typ události ("click", "mousedown", ...)
981  * @param {object || function} obj objekt, ve kterém se metoda nachází nebo připravená funkce
982  * @param {string || function} func název metody nebo instance funkce, která se má zavolat po té ,co je událost vyvolána
983  * @param {boolean} useCapture hodnota použitá jako argument capture pro DOM zachytávání
984  * @returns {JAX.Listener}
985  */
986 JAX.IListening.prototype.listen = function(type, obj, func, useCapture) {
987 	var eventFunc = null;
988 
989 	if (typeof(type) != "string") {
990 		console.error("JAX.IListening.listen: The first argument must be string describing event name. I got " + typeof(type));
991 		type = "";
992 	}
993 
994 	if (!obj) {
995 		console.error("JAX.IListening.listen: The second argument must be object or function. I got " + typeof(obj));
996 		eventFunc = function() {};
997 	}
998 
999 	if (typeof(obj) == "function" || (typeof(obj) == "object" && !func)) {
1000 		eventFunc = obj;
1001 	} else if (typeof(obj) == "object" && typeof(func) == "string") {
1002 		eventFunc = obj[func];
1003 
1004 		if (eventFunc) {
1005 			eventFunc = eventFunc.bind(obj);
1006 		} else {
1007 			console.error("JAX.IListening.listen: The third argument must be function or string with function name placed in object of second argument. I got " + func);	
1008 		}
1009 	} else if (typeof(obj) == "object" && typeof(func) == "function") {
1010 		eventFunc = func.bind(obj);
1011 	} else {
1012 		console.error("JAX.IListening.listen: The second argument must be object or function. I got " + typeof(obj));
1013 		eventFunc = function() {};
1014 	}
1015 
1016 	if (typeof(eventFunc) == "function") {
1017 		var f = function(e) {
1018 			eventFunc(new JAX.Event(e));
1019 		};
1020 	} else {
1021 		var f = {
1022 			handleEvent: function(e) {
1023 				eventFunc.handleEvent(new JAX.Event(e));
1024 			}
1025 		}
1026 	}
1027 	
1028 	this._node.addEventListener(type, f, useCapture);
1029 	var objListener = new JAX.Listener(this, type, f);
1030 
1031 	if (!JAX.IListening._listeners[type]) {
1032 		JAX.IListening._listeners[type] = [];
1033 	}
1034 
1035 	JAX.IListening._listeners[type].push(objListener);
1036 
1037 	return objListener;
1038 };
1039 
1040 /**
1041  * odvěsí posluchač na základě parametru, což může být jednak typ události ("click", "mousedown", ...) nebo lze předat instanci JAX.Listener. Metodu lze také zavolat bez parametrů a tím se odvěsí všechny posluchače na elementu.
1042  *
1043  * @param {string || object} listener typ události nebo instance JAX.Listener
1044  * @returns {JAX.Node}
1045  */
1046 JAX.IListening.prototype.stopListening = function(listener) {
1047 	if (!listener && arguments.length) {
1048 		console.error("JAX.IListening.stopListening: Argument must be string with event type or instance of JAX.Listener.");
1049 		type = "";
1050 	}
1051 
1052 	if (!arguments.length) {
1053 		for (var i in JAX.IListening._listeners) {
1054 			this.stopListening(i);
1055 		}
1056 		return this;
1057 	}
1058 
1059 	if (typeof(listener) == "string") {
1060 		var type = listener;
1061 		var listeners = JAX.IListening._listeners[type] || [];
1062 		var deleteIndexes = [];
1063 
1064 		for (var i=0, len=listeners.length; i<len; i++) {
1065 			var l = listeners[i];
1066 			if (l.jaxElm().n == this._node) {
1067 				this._node.removeEventListener(type, l.method());
1068 				deleteIndexes.push(i);
1069 			}
1070 		}
1071 
1072 		for (var i=0, len=deleteIndexes.length; i<len; i++) {
1073 			var deleteIndex = deleteIndexes[i];
1074 			listeners.splice(deleteIndex, 1);
1075 		}
1076 
1077 		return this;
1078 	} 
1079 
1080 	if (listener instanceof JAX.Listener && listener.method()) {
1081 		var type = listener.type();
1082 		this._node.removeEventListener(type, listener.method());
1083 
1084 		var listeners = JAX.IListening._listeners[type] || [];
1085 		var deleteIndex = listeners.indexOf(listener);
1086 
1087 		if (deleteIndex > -1) {
1088 			listeners.splice(deleteIndex, 1);
1089 		} else {
1090 			console.warn("JAX.IListening.stopListening: I did not find given listener object in my storage. You probably called new JAX.Listener in your code and that's not good practice. Use listen and stopListening method all the time.");
1091 		}
1092 
1093 		return this;
1094 	}
1095 
1096 	console.error("JAX.IListening.stopListening: For the first argument I expected instance of JAX.Listener, string with event type or you can call it without arguments to stop all events listening.");
1097 	return this;
1098 };

1416 			}
1417 		}
1418

1463 		if (/^[#.a-z0-9_-]+$/ig.test(node)) {
1464 			try {
1465 				var result = !!JAK.DOM.findParent(this._node, node); // FIXME - opravit v JAKu pro IE8
1466 				return result;

1468 				return false;

1470 		}
1471 		return !!JAX.all(node).filterItems(jaxElm.contains.bind(this, this)).length;
1472 	}

1475 	return jaxNode.n && jaxNode.contains(this);

1500 /** 
1501  * vrací následující node
1502  *
1503  * @param {string || number || undefined} selector řetězec splňující pravidla: tag#id.trida (lze zada více id i tříd) || požadovaný nodeType
1504  * @returns {JAX.Node || null}
1505  */
1506 JAX.IMoveableNode.prototype.next = function(selector) {
1507 	if (typeof(selector) == "number") {
1508 		var n = this._node.nextSibling;
1509 		while(n) {
1510 			if (n.nodeType == selector) {
1511 				return JAX(n);
1512 			}
1513 			n = n.nextSibling;
1514 		}
1515 		return null;
1516 	} else if (typeof(selector) == "string") {
1517 		var n = this._node.nextElementSibling;
1518 		if (/^[#.a-z0-9_-]+$/ig.test(selector)) {
1519 			while(n) { 
1520 				if (this._matches(n, selector)) {
1521 					return JAX(n);
1522 				}
1523 				n = n.nextElementSibling;
1524 			}
1525 		}
1526 		return null;
1527 	}
1528 
1529 	var n = this._node.nextSibling;
1530 	return n ? JAX(n) : null;
1531 };

1534  * vrací předchazející node
1535  *
1536  * @param {string || number || undefined} selector řetězec splňující pravidla: tag#id.trida (lze zada více id i tříd) || požadovaný nodeType
1537  * @returns {JAX.Node || null}
1538  */
1539 JAX.IMoveableNode.prototype.previous = function(selector) {

1546 			n = n.previousSibling;
1547 		}
1548 		return null;
1549 	} else if (typeof(selector) == "string") {
1550 		var n = this._node.previousElementSibling;
1551 		if (/^[#.a-z0-9_-]+$/ig.test(selector)) {
1552 			while(n) { 
1553 				if (this._matches(n, selector)) {
1554 					return JAX(n);
1555 				}
1556 				n = n.previousElementSibling;
1557 			}
1558 		}
1559 		return null;
1560 	}
1561 
1562 	var n = this._node.previousSibling;
1563 	return n ? JAX(n) : null;
1564 };

1566 JAX.IMoveableNode.prototype._matches = function(n, selector) {
1567 	var parts = (selector || "").match(/[#.]?[a-z0-9_-]+/ig) || [];
1568 	var ok = true;
1569 
1570 	for (var i=0;i<parts.length;i++) {
1571 		var part = parts[i];
1572 		switch (part.charAt(0)) {
1573 			case "#":
1574 				if (n.id != part.substring(1)) { ok = false; }
1575 			break;
1576 			case ".":
1577 				if (!JAK.DOM.hasClass(n, part.substring(1))) { ok = false; }
1578 			break;
1579 			default:
1580 				if (n.nodeName.toLowerCase() != part.toLowerCase()) { ok = false; }
1581 			break;
1582 		}
1583 	}
1584 	
1585 
1586 	return ok;
1587 };

1610 		return this;
1611 	}
1612 
1613 	if (typeof(nodes) == "string") {
1614 		if (this._node.insertAdjacentHTML) {
1615 			this._node.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", nodes);
1616 			return this;

1618 		
1619 		JAX.makeFromHTML(nodes).appendTo(this);
1620 		return this;
1621 	}
1622 		
1623 	JAX.all(nodes).appendTo(this);
1624 	
1625 	return this;

1636 		console.error("JAX.INodeWithChildren.insertFirst: My element can not have children.", this._node);
1637 		return this;
1638 	}
1639 
1640 	if (typeof(nodes) == "string") {
1641 		if (this._node.insertAdjacentHTML) {
1642 			this._node.insertAdjacentHTML("afterbegin", nodes);
1643 			return this;
1644 		} 
1645 	}
1646

1648 		var jaxNodes = JAX.makeFromHTML(nodes);
1649 	} else {

1655 	}
1656 
1657 	for (var i=0;i<jaxNodes.length; i++) {
1658 		var n = jaxNodes[i].n;
1659

1661 			this._node.insertBefore(n, this._node.firstChild);

1664 		}
1665 	}

1703  * @returns {boolean}
1704  */
1705 JAX.INodeWithChildren.prototype.contains = function(nodes) {
1706 	if (!nodes) { return false; }
1707 
1708 	if (typeof(nodes) == "string") {
1709 		return !!this.find(nodes).n;
1710 	}
1711 
1712 	var jaxNodes = JAX.all([].concat(nodes));
1713 
1714 	if (!jaxNodes.length) { return false; }
1715 
1716 	for (var i=0, len=jaxNodes.length; i<len; i++) {
1717 		var n = jaxNodes[i].n;
1718 		if (!n) { return false; }
1719 
1720 		if (this._node.contains && !this._node.contains(n)) {
1721 			return false;
1722 		} else {
1723 			if (!this._contains(n)) {
1724 				return false;
1725 			}
1726 		}
1727 	}
1728 	
1729 	return true;
1730 };

1738 JAX.INodeWithChildren.prototype.children = function(index) {

1740 		console.error("JAX.INodeWithChildren.children: My element can not have children.", this._node);
1741 		return new JAX.NodeArray([]);

1743

1745 		var childNodes = this._node.childNodes;
1746 		var length = childNodes.length;
1747 		var nodes = new Array(length);
1748 		
1749 		for (var i=0; i<length; i++) {
1750 			nodes[i] = JAX(childNodes[i]);
1751 		}
1752 		return new JAX.NodeArray(nodes);
1753 	}
1754 
1755 	var child = this._node.childNodes[index];
1756 	if (child) {
1757 		return JAX(child);
1758 	}
1759 
1760 	return null;
1761 };

1765  *
1766  * @param {number || undefined} index číselný index požadovaného elementu
1767  * @returns {JAX.Node || JAX.NodeArray || null}
1768  */
1769 JAX.INodeWithChildren.prototype.elements = function(index) {
1770 	if (!this._node.children && !this._node.childNodes) {
1771 		console.error("JAX.INodeWithChildren.elements: My element can not have any element.", this._node);
1772 		return new JAX.NodeArray([]);
1773 	}
1774 
1775 	var children = this._node.children || this._node.childNodes; /* IE8 - zahrnuje comment nody do children, Safari na mobilu nepodporuje u documentFragmentu children */
1776 	var length = children.length;
1777 
1778 	if (!arguments.length) {	
1779 		var elms = [];
1780 		
1781 		for (var i=0; i<length; i++) {
1782 			var child = children[i];
1783 			if (child.nodeType == 1) { elms.push(JAX(child)); }
1784 		}
1785 
1786 		return new JAX.NodeArray(elms);
1787 	}
1788 
1789 	var counter = 0;
1790 	for (var i=0; i<length; i++) {
1791 		var child = children[i];
1792 		if (counter == index) {
1793 			return JAX(child);
1794 		}
1795 		counter++;
1796 	}
1797 
1798 	return null;
1799 };

1845 JAX.INodeWithChildren.prototype._contains = function(node) {

2735 		var value = "";

2737 			value = match2;

2744 JAX.Element.prototype._getSizeWithBoxSizing = function(sizeType, value) {
2745 	var boxSizing = JAX.Node._BOX_SIZING ? this.computedCss(JAX.Node._BOX_SIZING) : "";
2746 
2747 	var paddingX = 0,
2748 		paddingY = 0,
2749 		borderX = 0,
2750 		borderY = 0,
2751 		paddingPropertyX = "padding-" + (sizeType == "width" ? "left" : "top"),
2752 		paddingPropertyY = "padding-" + (sizeType == "width" ? "right" : "bottom"),
2753 		borderPropertyX = "border-" + (sizeType == "width" ? "left" : "top"),
2754 		borderPropertyY = "border-" + (sizeType == "width" ? "right" : "bottom");
2755 
2756 	if (arguments.length == 1) {
2757 		var value = (sizeType == "width" ? this._node.offsetWidth : this._node.offsetHeight);
2758 	}
2759 
2760 	if (!boxSizing || boxSizing == "content-box") {
2761 		paddingX = parseFloat(this.computedCss(paddingPropertyX));
2762 		paddingY = parseFloat(this.computedCss(paddingPropertyY));
2763 	}
2764 	
2765 	if (boxSizing != "border-box") {
2766 		borderX = parseFloat(this.computedCss(borderPropertyX));
2767 		borderY = parseFloat(this.computedCss(borderPropertyY));
2768 	}
2769 	
2770 	if (paddingX && isFinite(paddingX)) { value -= paddingX; }
2771 	if (paddingY && isFinite(paddingY)) { value -= paddingY; }
2772 	if (borderX && isFinite(borderX)) { value -= borderX; }
2773 	if (borderY && isFinite(borderY)) { value -= borderY; }
2774 
2775 	return value;
2776 };

2782 		var tagName = child.tagName ? child.tagName.toLowerCase() : "";
2783 		if (child.childNodes && child.childNodes.length) { text += this._getText(child); continue; }
2784 		if (child.nodeValue) { text += child.nodeValue; continue; }
2785 		text += " ";
2786 	}
2787 	return text;

4412 JAX.FX.prototype.reverse = function() {
4413 	if (!this._canBeAnimated) { return new JAK.Promise.reject(this._jaxElm); }

4428 		var property = setting.property;
4429 		var method = setting.method;

4443 			var endValue = setting.endValue;

4456 		};
